{"tid":342442,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"想討論下操控 (今日第一次揸某牌子既車比佢嚇一嚇)","createTime":"2017-07-31T15:12:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T15:22:06.000Z","uid":119399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aac9e72f05dcb8c9a0b0f3eb95de06221ad98603","tid":342442,"uid":119399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:12:16.000Z","msg":"細佬我揸左7年幾車，擁有過4部車<br />\nRactis &gt; Stream 1.8 &gt; Forestor  &gt; 320D GT ( 揸左2 星期only)<br />\n如果呢4部比既話就無乜好講，GT一定贏，所以我主要想講日本車既操控<br />\n<br />\n話說我個friend去旅行成個月，佢架車拎左去噴油要我幫手拎，拎車仲要著埋油燈要我入油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁我緊係揸返百零K先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢架Mazda 3 2.0 2016年車，一坐上去個感覺已經唔係好似日本車，我唔識講點樣為之操控好，純粹個人感覺(軚感，轉向感覺) ，架車揸上手真係好好feel，老實講同自己架GT都差唔多，比自己揸過既3 架日本車比真係好太多，力方面就算係咁，始終自己揸左排turbo 同柴油車，感覺上mazda 3 係無乜力，個人感覺係<br />\n<br />\nmazda 3 &gt; forestor&gt;&gt;&gt;stream &gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; ractis<br />\n<br />\n以上純個人感覺，打手死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5806b21ebb469fc164efffc90de38429b3a0933","tid":342442,"uid":119399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:15:04.000Z","msg":"自膠開左2 個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a9042a4f885fa580b528f79329c91f58118094","tid":342442,"uid":75766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:20:32.000Z","msg":"Mazda 3 無力 油門好虛咁"},{"pid":"2c62540712cda87606e0962f77ad451efe9bc728","tid":342442,"uid":119399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T15:22:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Mazda 3 無力 油門好虛咁</blockquote><br />\n都係既，我野野踏到落底咁滯"}]}